               <head>Johannes Consobrinus, <title>De usura</title> and John Felton,
                     <title>Sermones</title></head>
               <physDesc>
                  <p><note>Comprising two originally separate MSS</note></p>
                  <objectDesc form="codex">
                     <supportDesc material="perg">
                        <support>both on vellum (the first FSOS/<term type="disposition">FHHF</term>, the second HSOS/<term type="disposition">HFFH</term>).</support>
                        <extent>Fols. <seg type="leaf"><measure type="laterEndleaf" quantity="3">iii</measure> + <measure type="leaf" quantity="40">40</measure> + <measure type="laterEndleaf" quantity="1">i</measure></seg> (numbered fol. 41) + 266 (numbered fols. 42–307)
